#########################################################################################
#											#
#			network probe utility						#
#											#
#########################################################################################


The probe utility app is used to find the nwetwork characteristics suh as latency,throughput and bandwidth

It is divided into two parts:

1.the probing app which runs in background

2.cli which is used to give user input


Th binaries for both cli and process are generated in bin directory  
CLI usage

1.For finding lateny

we can either give the URL or the ipaddress of to find latency value
-l option is used
e.g
./util -l www.google.com 
or
./util -l 192.168.10.12

2.   Throughput calculation
-t option is used
./util -t www.google.com
   or 
./util -t 192.168.10.12

3.banwidth ulilisation

-b option is used

./util -b eth0
